# Unity Project Specific
# -----------------
/[Vv][Rr] [Nn]etworking_[Bb]ack[Uu]p[Tt]his[Ff]older_[Bb]ut[Dd]ont[Ss]hip[Ii]t[Ww]ith[Yy]our[Gg]ame/
*[Bb]urst[Dd]ebug[Ii]nformation_[Dd]o[Nn]ot[Ss]hip/